And let's give 400
to the tens place.

00:03:38.070 --> 00:03:41.480
So let's give 400
to the tens place.

00:03:41.480 --> 00:03:44.630
Well, that'll make that 470.

00:03:44.630 --> 00:03:46.520
Let me do that in
