00:03:52.710 --> 00:03:56.881
And then I still have 200
to give to the ones place.

00:03:56.881 --> 00:03:57.630
So let me do that.

00:03:57.630 --> 00:04:02.240
So I still have 200 to
give to the ones place.

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:09.140
And so that's going
to go from 5 to 205.

00:04:09.140 --> 00:04:10.880
Once again, all
I've done is I've

00:04:10.880 --> 00:04:14.990
regrouped the value
in the number 675.

00:04:14.990 --> 00:04:17.334
Any of these still
represent 675.

00:04:17.334 --> 00:04:18.959
You can add these
numbers on the right.

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:21.600
They all add up to 675.

